OL,7,FThe next Prime Minister will have no  
OL,8,Fshortage of things to deal with.      
OL,10,FThe global impact of the war in       
OL,11,FUkraine, soaring inflation, rising    
OL,12,Fenergy costs, Brexit, the Northern    
OL,13,FIreland protocol, the recovery from the
OL,14,Fpandemic, the chance of another       
OL,15,FScottish independence referendum  the
OL,16,Flist goes on.                         
OL,18,FBroadcasting policy may seem like     
OL,19,Fsomething of a side issue, at least in
OL,20,Fthe short term.                       
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
OL,22,                                   G1/9
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
