OL,7,FOpponents of Channel 4's privatisation
OL,8,Fhad hoped the new Prime Minister might
OL,9,Fhave a change of heart. However this  
OL,10,Fseems increasingly unlikely.          
OL,12,FRishi Sunak has indicated that        
OL,13,Fprivatisation will go ahead if he wins.
OL,14,FAt the time of writing, Liz Truss has 
OL,15,Fnot said what she would do but her    
OL,16,Fbroader views on the role of the state
OL,17,Fwould appear to make a U-turn unlikely.
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
