OL,7,FTo people outside the media bubble, it
OL,8,Fmust have seemed strange to see Channel
OL,9,F4 privatisation flagged up by its     
OL,10,Fopponents as an issue in a Tory       
OL,11,Fleadership race brought about in such 
OL,12,Fdramatic circumstances at a difficult 
OL,13,Ftime for the country.                 
OL,15,FThose flagging it up in isolation     
OL,16,Frisked looking like they had tunnel   
OL,17,Fvision, though nobody should ever be  
OL,18,Fcondemned for highlighting an issue   
OL,19,Fwhich is important to them. Indeed bad
OL,20,Fdecisions can happen when an issue    
OL,21,Fisn't properly scrutinised.           
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
