OL,7,FHowever the whole Channel 4 debate    
OL,8,Fappears to have left the public       
OL,9,Fperplexed despite the passion of      
OL,10,FChannel 4's supporters, including many
OL,11,Findependent production companies.     
OL,13,FYet again, Channel 4 unwittingly did  
OL,14,Fitself no favours this week when      
OL,15,Freports emerged that staff were set to
OL,16,Freceive large bonuses to stay loyal.  
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
