OL,7,FOf course, Channel 4 Is commercially  
OL,8,Ffunded and is not part of the public  
OL,9,Fsector in the usual sense. However    
OL,10,Freports of the bonuses came as many   
OL,11,Fpublic sector workers  i.e., people  
OL,12,Fworking for the state or paid for out 
OL,13,Fof taxation  are warning of strikes  
OL,14,Fover pay rises well below inflation.  
OL,16,FMeanwhile Channel 4  like ITV and    
OL,17,FChannel 5  could be able to run more 
OL,18,Fadverts in the not too distant future.
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
