OL,7,FA different issue for the new PM, which
OL,8,Fis more likely to lead to a wide public
OL,9,Fdebate, is the future funding of the  
OL,10,FBBC. If the current licence fee       
OL,11,Fsettlement is the last, what could    
OL,12,Freplace it?                           
OL,14,FA House of Lords report this week ruled
OL,15,Fout advertising and subscription for  
OL,16,Fvery obvious reasons.                 
OL,18,FAdvertising would harm other          
OL,19,Fbroadcasters  subscription would mean
OL,20,Fthe BBC no longer delivered a service 
OL,21,Fto everyone.                          
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
OL,22,                                   G6/9
