OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1662210293
OL,7,FThe possible alternatives raised in the
OL,8,Freport are worthy of discussion in more
OL,9,Fdetail though.                        
OL,11,FA household levy would be paid by those
OL,12,Fwho don't have a TV but who listen to 
OL,13,Fthe radio or use the iPlayer. If it was
OL,14,Flinked to, say, council tax bands there
OL,15,Fwould be a broad link to somebody's   
OL,16,Fability to pay.                       
OL,18,FIt could also be collected with the   
OL,19,Fcouncil tax like water charges in     
OL,20,FScotland.                             
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
