OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1662210293
OL,7,FIt's also important to talk about how 
OL,8,Fmuch should be paid by pensioners,    
OL,9,Fstudents and those on low incomes.    
OL,11,FAll in all, nobody has ever pretended 
OL,12,Fthe TV Licence is a good way to fund  
OL,13,Fthe BBC  just the least worst.       
OL,15,FThe important thing is to ensure the  
OL,16,FBBC is not funded commercially, not   
OL,17,Ffunded out of government money and    
OL,18,Favailable to all free at the point of 
OL,19,Fuse. All ideas should be welcome.     
OL,3,CWhere are Channel 4 privatisation and 
OL,4,CBBC funding likely to sit in new Tory 
OL,5,Cagenda?                               
