OL,7,FHowever the issue of replacing the    
OL,8,Flicence fee can probably be parked    
OL,9,Funtil after the next General Election.
OL,11,FIt will be interesting to know what   
OL,12,Fideas the other parties may have or   
OL,13,Fwhether they would ultimately feel the
OL,14,Fcurrent system, for all its flaws, is 
OL,15,Fthe best option.                      
